sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin as User / Admin
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant PlatformOp as opendatahub-operator<br/>(Platform Operator)
    participant AIGO as ai-gateway-operator<br/>(Module Operator)
    participant BatchOp as batch-gateway-operator<br/>(Sub-Component)
    participant Operands as Batch Gateway Operands<br/>(API Server, Processor, GC)

    Note over PlatformOp,AIGO: Flow 1: Module Operator Reconciliation

    PlatformOp->>K8sAPI: Create AIGateway CR<br/>(default-aigateway)
    K8sAPI-->>AIGO: Watch event: AIGateway CR<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    AIGO->>AIGO: Load vendored manifests<br/>from /opt/manifests
    AIGO->>AIGO: Render kustomize overlays<br/>(ODH or RHOAI variant)

    alt spec.batchGateway.managementState = Managed
        Note over AIGO,BatchOp: Flow 2: Batch Gateway Sub-Component Lifecycle

        AIGO->>K8sAPI: Apply batch-gateway manifests<br/>(CRD + RBAC + Deployment)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI-->>BatchOp: Creates batch-gateway-operator<br/>Deployment + ServiceAccount

        Admin->>K8sAPI: Create LLMBatchGateway CR<br/>Auth: RBAC (llmbatchgateway-admin)
        K8sAPI-->>BatchOp: Watch event: LLMBatchGateway CR<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token

        BatchOp->>K8sAPI: Create API Server Deployment<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        BatchOp->>K8sAPI: Create Processor Deployment<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        BatchOp->>K8sAPI: Create GC Deployment<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        BatchOp->>K8sAPI: Create HTTPRoute CR<br/>(Gateway API)
        BatchOp->>K8sAPI: Create Certificate CR<br/>(cert-manager)
        BatchOp->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceMonitor<br/>(Prometheus)

        K8sAPI-->>Operands: Deployments created
    else spec.batchGateway.managementState = Removed
        AIGO->>K8sAPI: Delete batch-gateway resources
        Note over AIGO: Set DeploymentsAvailable=False<br/>Severity: Info (not Error)
    end

    AIGO->>K8sAPI: Update AIGateway CR status<br/>(version, build source,<br/>platform identity, manifest sources)
